### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@lessonId = 2b4a6ccd-4799-43ee-bd1d-63f76a04d14d
@courseId = 39ead153-e777-4be8-8f35-7dc44a3d3edd

### 1. Get Lesson with Content (PostgreSQL + MongoDB merged)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/content

### 2. Create Lesson Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/content
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lessonId": "{{lessonId}}",
  "videoUrl": "https://example.com/videos/intro-nestjs.mp4",
  "transcript": "In questa lezione introduciamo NestJS e la sua architettura modulare.",
  "attachments": [
    {
      "name": "Slide introduzione",
      "url": "https://example.com/attachments/intro-nestjs.pdf",
      "type": "pdf"
    },
    {
      "name": "Codice sorgente",
      "url": "https://example.com/attachments/intro-nestjs.zip",
      "type": "zip"
    }
  ],
  "quiz": [
    {
      "question": "Quale decoratore si usa per definire un controller in NestJS?",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "@Module()" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "@Controller()" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "@Injectable()" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "@Service()" }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "B"
    },
    {
      "question": "Quale ORM viene spesso usato con NestJS per PostgreSQL?",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "Mongoose" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "Sequelize" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "TypeORM" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "Prisma" }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "C"
    }
  ]
}

### 3. Update Lesson Content (campi parziali)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/content
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoUrl": "https://example.com/videos/intro-nestjs-v2.mp4",
  "transcript": "Trascrizione aggiornata della lezione."
}

### 4. Update solo quiz
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/content
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiz": [
    {
      "question": "Cosa fa il decoratore @Injectable()?",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "Definisce un controller" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "Marca una classe come provider iniettabile" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "Registra un modulo" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "Crea una route" }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "B"
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Update solo attachments
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/content
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attachments": [
    {
      "name": "Slide aggiornate",
      "url": "https://example.com/attachments/intro-nestjs-v2.pdf",
      "type": "pdf"
    }
  ]
}